p\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/t-mobile-spatula-giveaway.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/t-mobile-spatula-giveaway.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"1117\" height=\"861\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An image of a BBQ spatula T-Mobile plans to give away for T-Mobile Tuesdays.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/t-mobile-spatula-giveaway.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/t-mobile-spatula-giveaway.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eSource: The Mobile Report\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe carrier isn\u0026#39;t stopping at just a cookout tool, either, with more food-themed and seasonal benefits, including a Little Caesar\u0026#39;s discount, a Tastemade+ meal plan subscription deal, and some sort of special experience at the upcoming Fanatics Fest NYC sports event. Those are in addition to the typical discount on Shell gasoline.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eUnfortunately, the